<lb n="2" break="no"/><unclear>ru kīrtti</unclear> paṁḍitadēvarugaḷa nirūpadiṁda sārakhēti bhadradēvarugaḷa sadupadēśadiṁda<unclear>mū</unclear> vuḷiya baḷiya koṁtekiya maga kōṭe <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ḍida <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> biduriya nakarada yeṁṭumaṁdi seṭikāraru nālvaru yeḷamegaḷoḷagāda samasta halara Anujñeyiṁda [Ā] tribhuvanacūḍāmaṇiyeṁba
<lb n="4"/>caityālayada caṁdranāthasvāmigaḷa mahābhiṣēkārtthavāgi nirmmāpisida suvarṇnakuṁbhada tūka varaha ga
<lb n="5"/>45 <unclear>ga</unclear> Ø Idarabaṇna 10 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Idakke kraya varaha gadyāṇaṁ 500 Ī rītiya suvarṇnakuṁbhavanu caṁdranāthasvāmiya śrīpāda
<lb n="6" break="no"/>padmaṁgaḷige kāṇikeya māḍi Ācaṁdrārkkasthāyiyāgi kīrtti puṇyavanu vupārjjisi koṁḍaru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ī śāsanakke tappidavaru caṁ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>dranāthasvāmige tappidavaru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vujaṁtyagiriyalli sāvirajinabiṁbava naḷida dōṣaka hōharu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Aḷupabēkeṁ<unclear>du nena</unclear>davaru
<lb n="8"/>yi bhūmiyuḷakālakke <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> yiṁtī śāsanada vakkaṇe bidureya caṁdrama Upādhyāya barada <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> maṁgaḷa mahāśrī śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
